-- Jaiz of Nigeria Opens 3 Islamic Bank Branches, Vanguard Says
-- B y   C h r i s   K a y
-- 2012-02-16T08:50:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-16/jaiz-of-nigeria-opens-3-islamic-bank-branches-vanguard-says.html
Jaiz Bank Plc , a Nigerian Islamic
lender, started operations in three branches in the northern
cities of Kaduna, Kano and the capital, Abuja,  Vanguard
reported , citing unnamed bank officials.  To contact the reporter on this story:
